    "title": "Improve first-run reading time guidance",
    "body": "<!-- CURSOR_AGENT_PR_BODY_BEGIN -->\n## 変更点\n- 初回起動時に、現在のページの読了時間を自動見積もりする一言ガイドを表示\n- 本文テキストが見つからない空状態で、次に試す導線を表示\n- 初回ガイドの表示済みフラグを既存の storage アダプタ経由で保存し、core 側の型正規化に追加\n\n## build通過\n- `npm run build` 通過\n\n## permissions不変\n- `manifest.json` は変更なし\n- permissions は `activeTab`, `scripting`, `storage` のまま不変\n<!-- CURSOR_AGENT_PR_BODY_END -->\n\n<div><a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents/bc-b0a8eb19-2677-4b60-a27b-6ae99dbcccf6\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-light.png\"><img alt=\"Open in Web\" width=\"114\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-web-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/background-agent?bcId=bc-b0a8eb19-2677-4b60-a27b-6ae99dbcccf6\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-light.png\"><img alt=\"Open in Cursor\" width=\"131\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/open-in-cursor-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;</div>\n\n",
